'''波·戴姆倫'''（{{lang-en|Poe Dameron}}）是一名[[星際大戰|《星際大戰》專營權]]中的虛構人物，首次登場於2015年電影《[[STAR_WARS：原力覺醒|STAR WARS：原力覺醒]]》中，由[[奧斯卡·伊薩克|奧斯卡·伊薩克]]飾演。波·戴姆倫是一名抵抗勢力的[[X翼戰機|X翼戰機]][[王牌飛行員|王牌飛行員]]，在對抗[[第一軍團|第一軍團]]的過程中意外地認識了第一軍團叛逃的[[風暴兵|風暴兵]][[芬恩|芬恩]]（[[約翰·波耶加|約翰·波耶加]] 飾演）和{{link-en|賈庫星|Jakku}}的拾荒者[[芮|芮]]（[[黛西·蕾德莉|黛西·蕾德莉]] 飾演），尤其與前者的關係甚好。他出現在《STAR WARS：原力覺醒》的媒體、商品及同名漫畫書系列中，並於續集《[[STAR_WARS：最後的絕地武士|STAR WARS：最後的絕地武士]]》裡出現。伊薩克飾演的角色已獲得積極的評價。

== 角色 ==

=== 概念 ===

在《STAR WARS：原力覺醒》開發初期，該角色被稱作「John Doe」，並打算設計成一名[[絕地武士|絕地武士]]，並讓{{link-en|武技族|Wookiee}}的[[賞金獵人|賞金獵人]]與其搭檔<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.slashfilm.com/force-awakens-changes/ |title=How ''Force Awakens'' Changed During Development: Jedi Killers, Force Ghosts and The Doom Star |work={{link-en|/Film|/Film}} |first=Peter |last=Sciretta |date=2015-12-28 |accessdate=2015-12-28 |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123061535/https://www.slashfilm.com/force-awakens-changes/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 描繪 ===

伊薩克於電影中的角色在2014年4月29日首次宣布<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.starwars.com/news/star-wars-episode-vii-cast-announced |title=''Star Wars: Episode VII'' Cast Announced |publisher=[[星際大戰|StarWars.com]] |date=2014-04-29 |accessdate=2015-12-20 |archive-date=2016-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160213012837/http://www.starwars.com/news/star-wars-episode-vii-cast-announced |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他的角色在11月28日由[[盧卡斯影業|盧卡斯影業]]發布的88秒《STAR WARS：原力覺醒》前導預告片中首次亮相<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/videos/watch-star-wars-the-force-awakens-trailer-20141128 |title=Watch the Incredible ''Star Wars: The Force Awakens'' Trailer |work=Rolling Stone |date=2014-11-28 |accessdate=2016-01-01 |archive-date=2017-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171226182403/https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/videos/watch-star-wars-the-force-awakens-trailer-20141128 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Trailer Report: ''Star Wars'' Teaser Beats ''Age of Ultron'' In Debut |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/trailer-report-star-wars-teaser-753113?mobile_redirect=false |last=Lewis |first=Andy |work=[[好萊塢報導|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2014-12-01 |accessdate=2014-12-02 |archive-date=2015-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150306025753/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/trailer-report-star-wars-teaser-753113?mobile_redirect=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>，駕駛著X翼戰機<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2014/11/29/5-reasons-the-new-star-wars-trailer-was-the-perfect-first-glimpse-at-the-force-awakens/ |title=5 Reasons The New ''Star Wars'' Trailer Was The Perfect First Look At ''The Force Awakens'' |work=Forbes |first=Erik |last=Kain |date=2014-11-29 |accessdate=2016-01-01 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308201410/https://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2014/11/29/5-reasons-the-new-star-wars-trailer-was-the-perfect-first-glimpse-at-the-force-awakens/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/tv/tv-news/star-wars-force-awakens-trailer-4713536 |title=''Star Wars The Force Awakens'' trailer: 5 things we've learned from the EPIC ''Episode VII'' trailer |work=Daily Mirror |first=Tufayel |last=Ahmed |date=2014-11-28 |accessdate=2016-01-01 |archive-date=2016-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160213013721/http://www.mirror.co.uk/tv/tv-news/star-wars-force-awakens-trailer-4713536 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thewrap.com/star-wars-episode-vii-the-force-awakens-trailer-villain-millenium-falcon/ |title=''Star Wars: Episode VII – The Force Awakens'' Trailer Unmasks a Stormtrooper, Teases Villain |publisher=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]] |first=Greg |last=Gilman |date=2014-11-29 |accessdate=2016-01-01 |archive-date=2016-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160213013835/http://www.thewrap.com/star-wars-episode-vii-the-force-awakens-trailer-villain-millenium-falcon/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。波·戴姆倫的名字於12月由《[[娛樂周刊|娛樂週刊]]》在盧卡斯影業設計，{{link-en|Topps|Topps}}風格的[[交換卡片|交換卡片]][[Mockup|Mockup]]上發布<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/12/11/star-wars-the-force-awakens-character-names/ |title=''Star Wars: The Force Awakens'' character names revealed (in coolest way possible) |first=Anthony |last=Breznican |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2014-12-11 |accessdate=2014-12-11 |archive-date=2014-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141212030653/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/12/11/star-wars-the-force-awakens-character-names/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.starwars.com/films/star-wars-the-force-awakens-digital-trading-cards |title=''Star Wars: The Force Awakens'' Digital Trading Cards |publisher=StarWars.com |accessdate=2015-12-06 |archive-date=2016-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160213014323/http://www.starwars.com/films/star-wars-the-force-awakens-digital-trading-cards |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該角色是2015年5月在《[[浮華世界_(雜誌)|浮華世界]]》上的特色照片之一，其照片由[[安妮·萊柏維茲|安妮·萊柏維茲]]拍攝<ref name="VFCharacter">{{cite web|last=Robinson|first=Joanna|title=Adam Driver and Lupita Nyong'o's Characters Revealed in Exclusive ''Star Wars: The Force Awakens'' Photos|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2015/05/star-wars-force-awakens-photos|accessdate=2015-05-04|work=[[浮華世界_(雜誌)|Vanity Fair]]|date=2015-05-04|archive-date=2016-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160213014440/http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2015/05/star-wars-force-awakens-photos|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的名字源自於《STAR WARS：原力覺醒》的編劇/導演[[J·J·亞伯拉罕|J·J·亞伯拉罕]]的助理摩根·戴姆倫<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/exclusive-jj-abrams-assistant-morgan-dameron-oscar-isaac-poe-took-name/|title=J.J. Abrams' assistant reveals how Poe Dameron took her name|work=Empire|first=James|last=White|date=2015-12-03|accessdate=2015-12-20|archive-date=2021-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302195141/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/exclusive-jj-abrams-assistant-morgan-dameron-oscar-isaac-poe-took-name/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

